data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to your dream home! New Roof, Freshly painted & new carpet! This stunning single-level gem is the epitome of modern comfort and convenience, offering everything you could ever desire. With 3 bedrooms, an office, and a 2-car garage, this residence is the perfect blend of spaciousness and functionality. Upon entering, you'll be immediately drawn to the open floor plan that effortlessly connects the living room and kitchen, creating an inviting and inclusive atmosphere. The living room is both elegant and cozy, providing a welcoming space for family gatherings or entertaining friends. Natural light pours in through large windows, creating a warm and inviting ambiance.The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances that are not only beautiful but also highly functional. Meal prep and cooking will be a breeze in this well-appointed space. Imagine hosting dinner parties with ease and elegance! Step outside into the lovely backyard, a true oasis for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee on the patio or hosting a barbecue with friends, this backyard will become your favorite spot to unwind. This home is not only beautiful but also equipped with modern conveniences. The water heater and dishwasher were both replaced in 2022, ensuring worry-free living. Plus, the water softener is a fantastic addition for those who appreciate the benefits of soft, luxurious water. Located in a desirable community, residents here enjoy access to a refreshing pool – perfect for those hot summer days. You'll also appreciate the convenience of being close to shopping, dining, and entertainment options, making this location highly sought after. Welcome Home!
